        Parameters:
        author - Requester of the song.
        textChannel - Text channel it was requested in
        track - Track to play.
        Returns:
        Returns the status of the addition, can either be NOT_IN_VOICE which means the requester is not in a voice channel, ALREADY_IN_USE which means the bot is being used in another voice channel for that guild, or SUCCESS which means everything went smoothly.
